title: TinyMCE Advanced 4.2.3.1 - WordPress Plugins
description:
Enables the advanced features of TinyMCE, the WordPress WYSIWYG editor. This plugin will let you add, remove and arrange the buttons that are shown on the Visual Editor toolbar.It includes 15 plugins for TinyMCE that are automatically enabled or disabled depending on what buttons are chosen. Contains external links.

WP Requirements:
4.3 or higher, up to 4.3

To install:
1. Upload the folder to the /wp-content/plugins/ directory
2. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress
